n@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jeremy-allen-white-bruce-springsteen@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jeremy-allen-white-bruce-springsteen@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jeremy-allen-white-bruce-springsteen@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/jeremy-allen-white-bruce-springsteen@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-bear"><em>《熊》</em></a>明星杰里米·艾伦·怀特有望在一部即将上映的关于布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀 1982 年专辑《内布拉斯加》制作的电影中饰演<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bruce-springsteen">布鲁斯·斯普林斯汀</a>。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-features/music-biopics-best-to-see-before-you-die-3401944">生前值得一看的 50 部音乐传记片</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/03/bruce-springsteen-jeremy-allen-white-movie-scott-stuber-nebraska-scott-cooper-directing-a24-ellen-goldsmith-vein-1235868961/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>好莱坞截止日期报道</em></a>，怀特是最有可能在这部影片中扮演年轻的斯普林斯汀的人选。据报道，该片名为<em>《从无处拯救我</em>》，该片将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bruce-springsteen-reportedly-working-on-film-of-the-making-of-nebraska-3570491">今年一月上映</a>。 <em>Deadline</em>指出，与 White 的谈判尚未开始，受欢迎的电影公司 A24 正在就加入该项目进行谈判。 </p><figure id="attachment_3567316" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3567316" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3567316" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images.jpg" alt="杰里米·艾伦·怀特" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Allen-White-Golden-Globes-Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Jeremy-Alle